{"tid":2239973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈建議港人停工三日跟隨特首會面習總!!!","createTime":"2020-10-12T10:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T18:48:44.000Z","uid":225437,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb7758067a987c5f59425b554a63a320313aa07","tid":2239973,"uid":225437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:56:15.000Z","msg":"我地首長林鄭月娥女士因習總南巡深圳<br />\n擱置手頭上工作 直奔深圳會面習總<br />\n香港人應該效仿首長林鄭<br />\n放下手頭上工作 前往深圳一睹習總一面<br />\n正如首長所言 工作前最好徵求中央意見<br />\n香港人應在工作前與習總磋商 停工三日<br />\n以配合大灣區整體發展<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叫香港人罷工難過支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n工會又唔肯入 票又唔肯投<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭罷工你地都未肯罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0ec3ee744ca89c231d7e2516967cad870a2a21","tid":2239973,"uid":225437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:58:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae3fa946bf65d32bcd7c3bd8d873386e8d27602e","tid":2239973,"uid":225437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:00:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07dbe75cd6e789b0dac8a6c3b78c4a0416042b29","tid":2239973,"uid":225437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:03:02.000Z","msg":"真話冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876417ecc1d29371048e9c9021409d7da1e0e1b3","tid":2239973,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:05:10.000Z","msg":"所以聽日咪八號風球畀你囉"},{"pid":"290566de3ca46112e12f3dd0054b75552f1de80b","tid":2239973,"uid":225437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:23:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24cb7631b358eee